---
import Container from "./Container.astro"

---

<div class="text-gray-600 darkcanceltext-gray-300" id="testimonials">
  <Container>
    <div class="mb-20 space-y-4 px-6 md:px-0">
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 darkcanceltext-white md:text-4xl">
        We have some fans.
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="md:columns-2 lg:columns-3 gap-8 space-y-8">
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white darkcancelbg-gray-800 darkcancelborder-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 darkcancelshadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar.webp" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 darkcanceltext-white">Henrik Andersson</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 darkcanceltext-gray-300">Founder</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">Working with Ayush's team was exactly what we needed. They helped automate our website leads into HubSpot, and when we had questions about some custom fields, they jumped on a call to sort it out. Really appreciate the personal touch."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white darkcancelbg-gray-800 darkcancelborder-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 darkcancelshadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-1.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 darkcanceltext-white">Maria Lindstr√∂m</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 darkcanceltext-gray-300">Founder</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8"> Been working with them for about 8 months now. Started with just email automation but ended up redoing all our sales processes. Love how they keep checking in to make sure everything's running smoothly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white darkcancelbg-gray-800 darkcancelborder-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 darkcancelshadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-2.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 darkcanceltext-white">Laurent Dubois</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 darkcanceltext-gray-300">Developer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">Had a few hiccups initially with our complex setup, but the team stuck with us until everything was perfect. Now our departments actually talk to each other, and I don't spend my Fridays doing manual data entry anymore.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white darkcancelbg-gray-800 darkcancelborder-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 darkcancelshadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-3.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 darkcanceltext-white">Vibhor Sharma</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 darkcanceltext-gray-300">Agency Owner</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">Our business runs between three countries, so automation was a mess before. They set up our project management system to talk with our CRM, and my team finally stopped complaining about double data entry. It's the little things that make a huge difference.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white darkcancelbg-gray-800 darkcancelborder-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 darkcancelshadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-4.webp" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 darkcanceltext-white">Sushant Rajput</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 darkcanceltext-gray-300">Lead Gen Agency Owner</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8"> What I appreciate most is how they understood our specific needs. They didn't just set up some generic automation - they took time to learn our workflow and suggested solutions I hadn't even thought of. Plus, they're just genuinely nice people to work with.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white darkcancelbg-gray-800 darkcancelborder-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 darkcancelshadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/avatar-2.webp" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 darkcanceltext-white">Saurav Sharma</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 darkcanceltext-gray-300">Founder</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">I've recommended them to several colleagues already. They helped us build a custom lead routing system between our websites, sequencers and CRM.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </Container>
</div>